You can optionally enable code analyzers to enforce a consistent cleanup approach:

*   [MSTEST0021](mstest-analyzers/mstest0021) - Prefer Dispose over TestCleanup methods
*   [MSTEST0022](mstest-analyzers/mstest0022) - Prefer TestCleanup over Dispose methods

